data.description: Valparaiso home for sale with two bedrooms, two full baths a den/office and a two car attached garage. Upstairs there is a spacious unfinished attic ready for you to finish and put your own touch on which could be used as a third bedroom, craft room, rec room, use your imagination. Enjoy evenings on your back deck overlooking the pond with a fountain or for cooler months in the enclosed sun room/ porch. The large bright living room is open to the dining area. The main bedroom has a walk in closet and attached bath. There is a large pantry and laundry is conveniently located off the kitchen. Snow removal and lawn care are taken care of by the HOA association.
